text: Prolecanitidae is a family of ammonites in the order Prolecanitida, with 10 genera. = Genera = Genera placed by Fossilworks. * Becanites Korn, 1997 * Cantabricanites Weyer, 1965 * Dombarocanites Ruzhencev, 1949 * Eocanites Librovitch, 1957 * Katacanites Kullmann, 1963 * Merocanites Schindewolf, 1922 * Metacanites Schindewolf, 1922 * Michiganites Ruzhencev, 1962 * Prolecanites Mojsisovics, 1882 * Protocanites Schmidt, 1922 ==References== Category:Prolecanitida
title: Prolecanitidae
